Calamus 1.3.0

Based on: leafpad - A GTK+ based simple text editor
Version 1.3.0

Changes:
- inline spellcheck disabled
- F7 runs external interactive Hunspell spellcheck
- interactive Replace / Replace All / Ignore / Ignore All workflow
- Always on Top toggle retained
- optional White Background toggle
- persistent window size, opacity, last file, language, white background and top-most setting

Runtime spellcheck requirements:
- hunspell
- hunspell-it for Italian
- hunspell-en-us for English
Calamus 1.6.1: refreshed color icon for better visibility on dark themes.
